response.overview: CatVideoFest is a joyous communal experience, only in theaters, that raises money for local cats in need through partnerships with cat charities, animal welfare organizations, and shelters.  The annual family-friendly CatVideoFest is a compilation reel of cat videos culled from countless hours of unique submissions and sourced animations, music videos, and, of course, classic internet powerhouses.
response.title: Cat Video Fest 2025
